- `langgraph-graph-duality.md` — Competitive analysis of LangGraph (25.1k stars, Pregel-inspired). State-centric vs walker-centric graph philosophy. Durable execution, HITL, subgraph, memory gaps. Infrastructure vs intelligence ceiling thesis.
